  "text": "Hz, for the time window ∆t = 15 ns. With 400 PMT sets, this gives a background rate of roughly 300 events per year 7 . Additional strategies can be applied to further reduce the background as discussed in Ref. [CITATION_1] , but we directly take 300 events for the detector background of the nominal design of FerMINI as a rather conservative estimation of the background for the sensitivity projection.",
